# API Server Rules

## Structure
```
apps/api/
  prisma/schema.prisma   # DB schema
  src/
    routes/              # HTTP handlers, thin
    services/            # business logic
    middleware/          # auth, rate-limit
    db/prisma.js         # PrismaClient singleton
    validators/          # Zod schemas (co-locate or here)
```

## Data access
- Use `prisma` from `src/db/prisma.js` — no raw SQL unless necessary (`$queryRaw` for health checks only)
- Map Prisma camelCase to API camelCase in responses

## Auth
- Manager: username/password → JWT (15m) + httpOnly refresh cookie (30d, later)
- Cashier: PIN via `POST /auth/pin` with `X-Terminal-ID` + `X-Terminal-Secret`
- Validate `role` claim on every protected route

## Errors
```json
{ "error": { "code": "INVALID_CREDENTIALS", "message": "...", "request_id": "uuid" } }
```

## Logging
Fastify/Pino structured logs with `requestId`.
